def max_Prime_Factors(n):
  """Finds the largest prime factor of a given number.

  Args:
    n: An integer.

  Returns:
    The largest prime factor of n.
  """
  factors = []
  i = 2
  while i * i <= n:
    if n % i == 0:
      factors.append(i)
      n //= i
    else:
      i += 1
  if n > 1:
    factors.append(n)
  return max(factors)
```

